  <p style="font-size:14px;margin-bottom:0;"><strong>Type:</strong> Synthetic D-retro-inverso peptide &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Molecular Weight:</strong> ~2,200 Da &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Target:</strong> FOXO4-p53 interaction in senescent cells &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Origin:</strong> Dr. Peter de Keizer's lab, Erasmus University Medical Center &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Route:</strong> Injection (intraperitoneal in mice; likely subcutaneous in humans) &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Status:</strong> Research compound only, no human trials &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Primary Action:</strong> Selective senolysis via p53 reactivation</p>
